title: Innergie mCube Slim 95 95 Watt Universal AC Adapter with USB for Notebooks and Portable Devices (ADP-95BB AA)
description: If it's power you need, then with the Innergie mCube Slim 95, it is power you'll get. The ultra-compact design is stylish and powerful with a 95 watt output, compatible with most popular brand 18-21 volt laptops. In addition to the 95 watt power capability, there is also a 10 watt USB port for charging your iPad or other media devices. Ships with 9 connectors for different manufacturers and charger is energy efficient with multiple built-in protections.
